Description:
Imagine writing a story that has no end. That’s what we do every day–constantly evolve and hone our work to create something that’s timeless, effortless and universally accepted: design that’s for everyone.

Our goal is to curate a culture of visual inspiration, storytelling, and identity seeking. But, a physical space can only do so much, so we like to get out and explore. We think of our workspace as “wherever we are.”

// capabilities
We are a design studio specializing in branding development, logo design, print, packaging, web, mobile, interactive, copywriting, art direction, creative direction, email, and social media.

// anti-jargon philosophy
We won’t bore you with annoying industry buzzwords, because that’s not how we speak. Eighty-six the lingo and other industry vernacular.

// about the team
They say you’re only as good as the people you surround yourself with, and we couldn’t agree more. We love our people. Our goal is to curate a culture of visual inspiration, storytelling, and identity seeking.

Our studio, our people and our work are an ever-changing representation of the continuous and unexpected thoughts that inspire us to make things people love.

// custom-fit process
One single, templated process can’t work for every project. When it comes to creativity, there’s no magic theorem. The way we get there is always as unique as the final result. While the initial vision comes from you, your product and your passion, we do everything we can to dream with you, capture its essence and build work around it that exceeds everyone’s expectations.

Somos TOO LOVERS DESIGN,
un estudio de diseño gráfico con más de 10 años de experiencia en nuestro campo, ubicado en la ciudad de Alicante.

Adictos al café, a salir a pensar a la terraza mirando al sol con los ojos cerrados y estúpidamente enamorados de nuestra profesión. Pero sobre todo, somos afortunados de hacer lo que nos gusta y de hacerlo bien.

Nuestra trayectoria profesional se vuelca en proyectos integrales de branding de producto, naming, diseño de packaging y soluciones gráficas que garanticen la eficacia de un producto en el mercado.

Estamos abiertos a cualquier proyecto sea cual sea su ámbito o embergadura. Más que un estudio de diseño gráfico, somos una forma de pensar, de diseñar y de responder a las necesidades de nuestro cliente, implicándonos en su proyecto hasta el final.

Queremos compartir y desarrollar sus objetivos, impulsando la comunicación eficaz y favoreciendo estrategias integrales que posibiliten el crecimiento de su empresa.
Especialidades

-Packaging;

-Branding de Producto;

-Identidad Corporativa;

-Diseño Editorial;

- Diseño web.

The Unicorn is a boutique branding and animation agency specializing in transforming businesses into powerful brands. We tailor a unique brand’s essence with solid concepts, ideas, analytics and a deep business-oriented approach. 

Having successful experience with US, Australian, Canadian and European customers, we give you what AI can’t — an emotional connection, human understanding, and a deep business-oriented approach. 

List of our Services: 
- brand strategy (positioning, brand marketing), branding, rebranding;
- visual identity: logo, stationery, collateral, digital design material, guidelines;
- UI/UX for web and apps; 
- pitch decks and presentations; 
- 2D & 3D motion design: promo, explainers, interface, character-based animation, 
- traditional & cel animation; 
- Lottie JSON animations for apps and websites.

More than 12 years working on building and developing brands with personality and differentiation through strategic design and with a collaborative methodology with our customers that bring strong brands to live.

